HermesOS Genesis is an independent integration and bootstrap project.

This repository contains HermesOS/HKP additions and metadata alongside
upstream-derived patch context for Hermes Agent. Hermes Agent is an upstream
project of Nous Research. Upstream code, copyrights, and MIT license notices
remain the property of their respective authors and must be preserved.

HermesOS Genesis does not claim ownership of Hermes Agent or Nous Research
upstream code. The `bootstrap/` and `source_bundle/` materials identify
upstream-derived content through their manifests, provenance records, and
patch paths. HermesOS/HKP-specific additions are identified as custom runtime
files, bootstrap tooling, and project documentation.
